node.text:
The sight of lightning is undeniably majestic. Here are a few lightning strikes during last night thundery shower in Singapore.

#hellofrom #singapore🇸🇬 #monsoonseason #lightningstrike #thisissingapore #visitsingapore #travelfromhome #singaporeweather #qorz #stayhomeforsg #sgunited
@ben.pinto Thank you Ben! Happy Friday to you.
Wow😍😍 caught them at the right time!
Very high voltage shots! Thanks Javan!⚡❤-Eugene
Wow to all these lightning shots! Excellent series and a happy weekend bro 💯🔝🙌🏼⚡️
@ruycorto Thanks mate! Have a wonderful weekend. 🤗
@javan thank you Javan same to you
really amazing captures of the lightning 😍
😂 the secret tier is to be close enough to the lighting, back in a safe and dry place at the same time💙💙💙 great captures and wonderful editing😊
